botResponse: # Mojo Caller ID **Mojo Caller ID** is a virtual number service that provides you with an alternative caller ID for outbound calls while ensuring you still receive return calls on your phone. ## Key Details - **Cost**: $10 per month per number - **Billing**: Month-to-month subscription - **Purpose**: Use a personalized, professional caller ID instead of your personal number ## Key Benefits ### STIR/SHAKEN Certification Mojo Caller ID comes with the **highest STIR/SHAKEN attestation level A**, which means: - Your calls are verified as authentic and legitimate - Recipients recognize your calls as trustworthy - **Higher contact rates** due to reduced spam blocking - Calls are less likely to be flagged or ignored ### Professional Appearance - Projects professionalism and builds trust - Accurately identifies you to call recipients - Eliminates concerns about using personal phone numbers for business ## How It Works When you make calls through Mojo with Caller ID enabled, recipients see your chosen Mojo Caller ID number instead of your personal phone. However, if they call back, the call still comes to your actual phone. ## Getting Started You'll need to configure your Caller ID in your Mojo settings before using the Power Dialer. Check out the [Caller ID Configuration guide](https://mojodialersupport.mojosells.com/portal/en/kb/articles/caller-id-configuration) for setup instructions. **Need help with setup or have questions about Mojo Caller ID?** Let me know what specific aspect you'd like assistance with!
